prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon slice of pepperoni pizza, looking slightly frazzled and overwhelmed, is comically buried under a massive pile of brightly colored birthday candles that are all lit and dripping wax onto its cheesy surface. The pizza slice has wide, googly eyes and a silly, open-mouthed expression of surprise. Centered on the card, below the pizza, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the pizza and flames.
